{"tid":1154183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"依個環保廣告浪費咗幾多膠？","createTime":"2019-05-14T06:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T15:10:22.000Z","uid":1121,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a2de4c7bcb4fc6fe0702bd5c50b2fd2251fb15","tid":1154183,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jBdYkVyGOec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjBdYkVyGOec&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=48bf3564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jBdYkVyGOec</a><br />\n<br />\n地球因為依段廣告又短幾年命😭😭😭😭😭😭"},{"pid":"9eee22963d89d0be2366a4882ee5100b1fc38489","tid":1154183,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190513/large/1557759398_7cbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190513%2Flarge%2F1557759398_7cbd.jpg&h=30110fe8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e491147415f80319384a9da78774cc414b247019","tid":1154183,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190513/large/1557759401_3105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190513%2Flarge%2F1557759401_3105.jpg&h=4ac34a05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87ade60b9e30694af00f7d8daa9bb75e87fa3be7","tid":1154183,"uid":1121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"為愛地球、為環保，潮流興走塑；但不是得個講字，要真正有行動才可以。致力教育公眾減少使用塑膠的非牟利團體Eco Drive與促進香港青年發展的本地慈善機構香港新活力青年智庫合作，推出「不要膠下去」活動，並將訂立2019年5月30日為香港首個「無膠日」。<br />\n<br />\n今次這個走塑行動，獲得著名攝影師夏永康及60位名人及藝人的支持，其中負責配旁白的林海峰，今日在IG貼出宣傳片，參演者包括任賢齊、郭富城、楊千嬅、鄭秀文、梁詠琪（GiGi）、張智霖袁詠儀（靚靚）夫婦、甄子丹、葉德嫻（Deanie）、林嘉欣、吳君如和劉嘉玲。當中千嬅、靚靚及GiGi分別被膠樽蓋、即棄餐具及即棄食物容器兜頭淋，他們更要keep住無耐表情，不可動彈。"},{"pi